snippet.title: The beginning of the Race
snippet.description: We have started building out our race tracks for hover bike racing inside of Rocket Monsters. We offer a unique multiplayer within RMU, there is PVP battle and racing within the game. This is coupled with 4 very large sectors of land where players can build.
